  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下物流系统的核心流程，从配送路线开始。整个系统应该围绕DeliveryRoute、FleetManagement和TrackingNumber这几个核心模块展开。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那我把DeliveryRoute作为起点，然后直接连到FleetManagement？这两个模块之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，配送路线需要先经过车队管理。然后FleetManagement会触发一个关于TrackingNumber的判断节点，用来检查是否有有效的追踪单号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把DeliveryRoute画成起始节点，用浅蓝色标识，然后连接到FleetManagement，再引出TrackingNumber的判断菱形。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "TrackingNumber这个判断需要分两支：如果没有单号，走No分支，需要回到FleetManagement重新调度；如果有单号，走Yes分支继续往下走。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "No分支回到FleetManagement，这个我理解。但Yes分支接下来应该到哪里？需要进入仓库环节吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Yes分支要进入Warehouse的判断，检查货物是否在仓库中。这个节点很关键，决定了后续的流程走向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Warehouse判断节点。那如果货物不在仓库，也就是No分支，应该怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "No分支说明货物还没入库，需要回到TrackingNumber重新核实，可能是单号信息有误。这个路径用红色标识，表示异常流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Warehouse的No分支指向TrackingNumber，标记为异常。那Yes分支呢，货物在仓库的话？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Yes分支还需要再做一次TrackingNumber的复核，确认单号状态是否正常。这里又是一个判断点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_TrackingNumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
